{"tid":1882263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★實惠員工放無薪假 未來或關更多分店","createTime":"2020-02-16T06:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T07:16:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44887cacc3eec4c121de25013a5e2751b0a28379","tid":1882263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，令零售市道步入寒冬。專售傢私及家居用品的實惠集團表示，過去9個月已採取一系列減省成本措施，包括裁減10%分店人手，而2月起至5月期間，後勤員工要參與放無薪假，中及高級管理層減薪平均20%等，集團執行董事則減薪40%。<br />\n<br />\n實惠旗下亦有4間分店已停業，並表明正積極審視縮減更多分店，包括本年度租約屆滿的8間分店。實惠又指，未來或再裁員，期望業主減租，共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/435323/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%AF%A6%E6%83%A0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87-%E5%9F%B7%E8%91%A3%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%88%96%E9%97%9C%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F435323%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2583%25A0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%2591%25A3%25E6%25B8%259B%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=7228f915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/435323/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%AF%A6%E6%83%A0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87-%E5%9F%B7%E8%91%A3%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%88%96%E9%97%9C%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97</a>"},{"pid":"ffeea562102ba247340520f84e7381e3fd78e2b4","tid":1882263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:41:11.